{"tid":2160911,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳志全（慢必）：我不是「主留派」","createTime":"2020-08-17T09:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T15:27:07.000Z","uid":59818,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b791fd1839666be45a3048af9d1ec2977f05348a","tid":2160911,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5iD4req.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5iD4req.jpg&h=dcc9fae6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c172aaff28eb759d6ff19c44a6a5089d76666bd","tid":2160911,"uid":59818,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:15:04.000Z","msg":"朱凱迪：支持集體杯葛「臨立會」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2159636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2159636</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區朱凱迪：支持集體杯葛「臨立會」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2159636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2159636</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6d57f1d38ce19641003c3d019a8f02c8337617f7","tid":2160911,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5d702afd8327d7e7bc9e6ce1db5c9f39f52f9b","tid":2160911,"uid":59818,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:16:14.000Z","msg":"梁晃維 Fergus Leung <br />\n【致梁家傑：我想收翻民意授權，只係冇機會】<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">公民黨主席 Alan Leong Kah-Kit 梁家傑 喺上星期六出席港台節目嘅時候提到，「選民並無收回對民主派嘅授權」，因此接受人大委任嘅議員仍然擁有民意授權代表香港市民。</span><br />\n<br />\n我諗梁大狀必須要搞清楚一個概念，市民唔係冇收回授權，只係冇機會去收。從初選嘅結果我哋已經睇到，若果選舉如期進行，有唔少現任議員都可能未能連任。事實上，經歷四年來嘅風風雨雨，有唔少選民都已經為自己四年前嘅選擇而感到後悔，我就係一個好例子。<br />\n<br />\n16年嘅時候，民間呼籲「一票不投民主黨」，我最終喺超區投咗比梁耀忠。而唔駛等四年，16年開第一次大會，梁耀忠以「唔鍾意做主席」為由離席，將立法會主席之位拱手相讓比梁君彥，我已經後悔不已，即刻想搵窿捐。作為選民，投錯票揀錯人，被懲罰四年可以話冇得怨，但四年之期已到，梁耀忠仲憑乜繼續去代表多香港人一年，擔任所謂嘅議員？<br />\n<br />\n根據2016年選民嘅認知，下次選舉將會喺四年之後舉行，因此佢哋嘅一票只係支持當選人擔任代議士四年，第六屆立法會嘅民意授權亦將會喺2020年9月30日結束。套用梁大狀嘅諗法，如果冇選舉就可以延長民意授權的話，他朝一日出現「萬年國代」，香港唔再有選舉嘅時候，未知梁大狀會否因為中國政府繼續委任第六屆立法會全體議員，而認為「萬年國代」具有民意授權同正當性呢？"},{"pid":"ac01bd3f7bae2c342b3a7ba8a3b782119bbd9500","tid":2160911,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d57f1d38ce19641003c3d019a8f02c8337617f7","tid":2160911,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251407b0dfb3e147dc7206b19f4de62317de7df6","tid":2160911,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7853e8a903e3e2f7e8f273c049907779d5b12bb","tid":2160911,"uid":94516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:18:30.000Z","msg":"理泛狗會唔會屌慢必分裂5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ca33a60a65861d3af5672c8d158588c0fdcc07","tid":2160911,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca81a11bc2a5628cfab11589c77e9ad3cf327c3",